"title": "5082: Adam, significance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5082",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Throughout the NT, Adam is seen as a real historical figure, from whom all humanity is descended and by whose sin all humanity is affected.</p>\n<h2>Adam as the original member of the human race</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45-1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:45–15:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23-Luke3:38\">LUK 3:23–3:38</a> <em>The genealogy of Jesus Christ is traced back to Adam.</em></p>\n<h2>Adam's relationship with Eve</h2>\n<h3>Adam as one flesh with Eve</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:3-Matt19:6\">MAT 19:3–19:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:2-Mark10:9\">MRK 10:2–10:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:31\">EPH 5:31</a></p>\n<h3>Adam as the head of Eve</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:3\">1CO 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:8-1Cor11:12\">1CO 11:8–11:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:12-1Tim2:15\">1TI 2:12–2:15</a></p>\n<h2>The reality and results of Adam's sin</h2>\n<h3>Sin spread to all the human race</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:3-Gen4:16\">GEN 4:3–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:5\">PSA 51:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:9\">PRO 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></p>\n<h3>Death was introduced into the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:14-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:14–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21-1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:21–15:22</a></p>\n<h3>Condemnation for the human race resulted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16\">ROM 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:18\">ROM 5:18</a></strong></p>",
